{"tha-ap453:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap453:0.2":"Jagatidayakavagga ","tha-ap453:0.3":"Jagatidayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap453:1.1":"“Dhammadassissa munino, ","tha-ap453:1.2":"bodhiya padaputtame; ","tha-ap453:1.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap453:1.4":"jagatim karayim aham. ","tha-ap453:2.1":"Darito pabbatato va, ","tha-ap453:2.2":"rukkhato patito aham; ","tha-ap453:2.3":"Cuto patittham vindami, ","tha-ap453:2.4":"jagatiya idam phalam. ","tha-ap453:3.1":"Na me cora vihesanti, ","tha-ap453:3.2":"natimannanti khattiya; ","tha-ap453:3.3":"Sabbamittetikkamami, ","tha-ap453:3.4":"jagatiya idam phalam. ","tha-ap453:4.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap453:4.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap453:4.3":"Sabbattha pujito homi, ","tha-ap453:4.4":"jagatiya idam phalam. ","tha-ap453:5.1":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap453:5.2":"jagatim karayim aham; ","tha-ap453:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap453:5.4":"jagatidanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap453:6.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap453:6.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap453:6.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap453:6.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap453:7.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap453:7.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","tha-ap453:7.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap453:7.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap453:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap453:8.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap453:8.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap453:8.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap453:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma jagatidayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap453:10.1":"Jagatidayakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}